==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Builder
<hw>Build"er</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who builds; one
whose occupation is to build, as a carpenter, a shipwright, or a
mason.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In the practice of civil architecture, the <qex>builder</qex>
comes between the architect who designs the work and the artisans who
execute it.</q> <rj><qau>Eng. Cyc.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Building</ent>⟦br⟧
